description "IG-series Assassin Droid 

A sturdy and heavily armored gunner. 

^2Weaponry:
- Melee
-- 15% slower Movement
- Droid Slappers (Red Saber)
-- No Saber/Blaster Block
-- No Saber Training
-- 150% more Kb
-- 200% Spec Dmg mult
-- 35% less Reach
-- 300% more Radius
- Dual Blaster Rifles (WESTARs 4)
-- 35% slower RoF
-- 10% less Dmg
-- 15% less FP Dmg
- Thermal Detonator (1)
- Sonic Detonators (2)

^5Powers:
- Radar Scanner (Sense 1)

^8Attributes:
- 25% faster Hacking
- 20% less Kb Taken
- Recharge (3)
-- Resource Regen: 10/10s
- Strength (2)
- Environmental Protection (1)
- Beskar (3)
- Blast Armor
- Physical Resist
- Armor Regen (1)
- Sense Immunity
- Anti-Mind Trick (2)
- Tracking Beacon"